#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_strategy
msgid ""
"Describe all the key resources your company relies on to deliver its\n"
"                                business\n"
"                                model (financial, industrial, intellectual, "
